"<div dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Bitstream Vera Serif&#39;,&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;font-size:medium\">Looking for a long-term house sitter? </span><br style=\"font-family:&#39;Bitstream Vera Serif&#39;,&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;font-size:medium\"><br style=\"font-family:&#39;Bitstream Vera Serif&#39;,&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Bitstream Vera Serif&#39;,&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;font-size:medium\">29-year-old yoga-teaching, good-food-cooking, self-helpy-book-reading, introvert-at-heart who only plans to be in the area through this fall &amp; winter is looking for housing starting ASAP in the Upper Valley. </span><br style=\"font-family:&#39;Bitstream Vera Serif&#39;,&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;font-size:medium\"><br style=\"font-family:&#39;Bitstream Vera Serif&#39;,&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Bitstream Vera Serif&#39;,&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;font-size:medium\">I am not looking to get locked into a lease with another apartment &amp; all that hoopla, but am trying to find a way to be able to stay in the area for a few more months. So I am looking for a house-sitting opportunity through the fall &amp; winter where I can be of help to someone else while simultaneously having a roof over my head!</span><br style=\"font-family:&#39;Bitstream Vera Serif&#39;,&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;font-size:medium\"><br style=\"font-family:&#39;Bitstream Vera Serif&#39;,&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Bitstream Vera Serif&#39;,&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;font-size:medium\">I can provide excellent references, as well as the promise to keep your happy home in excellent condition while you&#39;re away - and even look after pets as needed. (A furry friend to snuggle once the snow flies would be very welcome!)</span><br style=\"font-family:&#39;Bitstream Vera Serif&#39;,&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;font-size:medium\"><br style=\"font-family:&#39;Bitstream Vera Serif&#39;,&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Bitstream Vera Serif&#39;,&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;font-size:medium\">If you - or someone you know - has an opportunity that would suit this, please reach out! I&#39;ll look forward to hearing from you :) </span><br style=\"font-family:&#39;Bitstream Vera Serif&#39;,&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;font-size:medium\"><br style=\"font-family:&#39;Bitstream Vera Serif&#39;,&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Bitstream Vera Serif&#39;,&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;font-size:medium\">&lt;&lt; If you happen to know of a month-by-month VERY low-cost rental opportunity I would love to hear about it too! Greatly appreciate your help! &gt;&gt;</span><br>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background: transparent; border: none; clear: both; display: block; float: none; position: static\"><br/>---------------------------<br/>Visit www.hartford-VT.org for town government information.<br/>Visit <a href=\"http://www.hsdvt.com/\">http://www.hsdvt.com/</a> for town schools information.<br/><br/>You received this message as a subscriber on the <a href=\"mailto:hartford@lists.vitalcommunities.org\">hartford@lists.vitalcommunities.org</a> discussion list.<br/><br/>To reach the list administrators please email <a href=\"mailto:hartford-request@lists.vitalcommunities.org\">hartford-request@lists.vitalcommunities.org</a> . Please DO NOT send help requests to the general list.<br/><br/>When posting, keep it specific to the town - please sign your posts - limit commercial postings to once a month - keep your tone civil and respectful.<br/><br/>When replying to a posting, if you receive the list digest, use the &quot;Reply to sender&quot; or &quot;Reply to list&quot; links at the end of the individual message. If you receive each posting as a separate email, use your mail p